<mxfile host="app.diagrams.net">
  <diagram name="Trang-1" id="AAIvdWaikjS7hFGzl4Ta">
    <mxGraphModel dx="2852" dy="2753" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="827" pageHeight="1169" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&quot;data&quot;:&quot;@startuml\nleft to right direction\n\n&#39; --- Tinh chỉnh khoảng cách cho thưa và thoáng ---\nskinparam roundcorner 10\nskinparam nodesep 40      \nskinparam ranksep 150     \nskinparam packageStyle rectangle\n\n&#39; --- BẮT BUỘC PASSENGER BÊN TRÁI ---\nactor \&quot;Passenger\&quot; as passenger\n\n&#39; --- KHUNG HỆ THỐNG TVM Ở GIỮA ---\nrectangle \&quot;Ticket Vendor Machine (TVM) System\&quot; as tvm {\n    package \&quot;1. Core Ticketing\&quot; {\n        usecase \&quot;Select Language\&quot; as UC_Lang\n        usecase \&quot;Start &amp; Select Destination\&quot; as UC_Dest\n        usecase \&quot;Calculate Fare\&quot; as UC_Fare\n        usecase \&quot;Print Ticket\&quot; as UC_Ticket\n    }\n\n    package \&quot;2. Payment Processing\&quot; {\n        usecase \&quot;Make Payment\&quot; as UC_Pay\n        usecase \&quot;Pay via Credit Card\&quot; as UC_PayCC\n        usecase \&quot;Pay via QR Code\&quot; as UC_PayQR\n        usecase \&quot;Validate Payment\&quot; as UC_Validate\n        usecase \&quot;Print Receipt\&quot; as UC_Receipt\n        usecase \&quot;Cancel Transaction\&quot; as UC_Cancel\n    }\n\n    package \&quot;3. System &amp; Maintenance\&quot; {\n        usecase \&quot;Handle Errors &amp; Refund\&quot; as UC_Error\n        usecase \&quot;Remote Monitoring\&quot; as UC_Monitor\n        usecase \&quot;Transaction Logging\&quot; as UC_Log\n    }\n}\n\n&#39; --- BẮT BUỘC EXTERNAL ACTORS BÊN PHẢI ---\nactor \&quot;Payment Gateway\\n(Visa, MoMo...)\&quot; as gateway &lt;&lt;External&gt;&gt;\nactor \&quot;Maintenance Staff\&quot; as staff\nactor \&quot;Central System\&quot; as cms &lt;&lt;External&gt;&gt;\n\n&#39; Ép các Actor bên phải nằm thẳng hàng dọc với nhau\ngateway -[hidden]d- staff\nstaff -[hidden]d- cms\n\n&#39; --- ĐIỀU HƯỚNG MŨI TÊN (TỪ TRÁI QUA) ---\npassenger ---&gt; UC_Lang\npassenger ---&gt; UC_Dest\npassenger ---&gt; UC_Pay\npassenger ---&gt; UC_Cancel\n\n&#39; --- SỬA LẠI CÁC LIÊN KẾT NỘI BỘ (Để hệ thống tự bo góc tự nhiên) ---\nUC_Dest ..&gt; UC_Fare : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n&#39; Đổi thành &lt;.. để PlantUML tự sắp xếp mà không bị gãy góc\nUC_Pay &lt;.. UC_PayCC : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\nUC_Pay &lt;.. UC_PayQR : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\nUC_Pay ..&gt; UC_Validate : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\nUC_Pay ..&gt; UC_Ticket : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt; (success)\n\nUC_Ticket &lt;.. UC_Receipt : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt; (for CC)\nUC_Cancel &lt;.. UC_Error : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt; (printer error)\n\n&#39; --- ĐIỀU HƯỚNG MŨI TÊN (SANG PHẢI) ---\nUC_Validate ---&gt; gateway\nUC_Error ---&gt; staff\nUC_Monitor ---&gt; staff\nUC_Monitor ---&gt; cms\nUC_Log ---&gt; cms\n\n@enduml&quot;,&quot;format&quot;:&quot;svg&quot;}" id="Cub3_2C1NXpBvyGhSPBt-1">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="836" width="2422" x="110" y="-240" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>
